Typedef Documentation

typedef struct QSPIFlash_HWCfg_t QSPIFlash_HWCfg

QSPI flash H/W Parameters.

QSPI flash parameters are used with the QSPIFlash_open() call.

typedef struct QSPIFlash_Params_t QSPIFlash_Params

QSPIFlash Parameters.

QSPI flash Parameters are used to with the QSPIFlash_open() call. Default values for these parameters are set using QSPIFlash_Params_init().
